snippet.title: Mob Wars: La Cosa Nostra | MMO RPG Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Mob Wars: La Cosa Nostra is a MMO RPG text based game where you enter a world of money, crime, corruption and mobsters. Play with 2+ million players!
